This example shows of a few HTML/Javascript features, along with an SQL example

You must have python/bottle/sqlite installed to run the full examples.

Instruction for Ubuntu 14.04 LTS. Run these commands(Some may have to be run as sudo):

#Install sqlite3
apt-get install sqlite
apt-get install python-sqlite

#Install Pip
wget https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py
python get-pip.py

#Install bottle
pip install bottle


Then, run:

python2 server.py

Go to localhost:8080, and the sample webpage should appear


